361
00:32:21.770 --> 00:32:23.170
Photosynthesis.

362
00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:27.200
-Good. Photosynthesis.
-What?

363
00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:28.360
What?

364
00:32:29.670 --> 00:32:31.410
lt's carried out
by many different organisms...

365
00:32:31.410 --> 00:32:33.640
